tests.title: Verify Coupon Code :- SaleSeptember
tests.fullTitle: Coupon test scenarios Verify Coupon Code :- SaleSeptember
tests.context: "assets/couponTest/CouponModuleTest.js/Coupon test scenarios -- Verify Coupon Code :- SaleSeptember (failed).png"
tests.code:
//visit Product page URL
cy.visit(coupon.productPageURL); //Add the product to the cart
_ProductDetailsPageTask.default.clickOnAddToCart; //verify the success message for Add to cart fuctionality
_ProdcutDetailsPageVerification.default.verifyAddtoCartSuccessMessage("Product successfully added to cart"); //verify view cart count 

_ProdcutDetailsPageVerification.default.verifyCartCount("1"); //click on view cart link

_ProductDetailsPageTask.default.clickOnViewCartLink(); //test for coupon code
//add coupon code to Coupon/Referral Code textBox

_ShoppingCartPageTask.default.addCouponCodeToCouponCodeBox(coupon.couponCode); //click apply button

_ShoppingCartPageTask.default.clickOnApplyCouponCodeButton(); //verify success message in the Popup alert

_ShoppingCartPageVerification.default.verifyCouponCodeSuccessMessagePopUP(coupon.verificationMessage); //verify success message displayed on the form

_ShoppingCartPageVerification.default.verifySuccessCouponMessage(coupon.verificationMessage);
